<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的平安夜，<delay20 />
我收到了<delay8 />圣诞老人送的礼物，<delay20 />
而且是我之前就祈祷想要收到的东西～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直很担心圣诞老人<delay8 />
会不会没有注意到我的请求，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来他确实有听到呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">收到圣诞老人送我的礼物后，
我实在太高兴了，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天晚上都没怎么睡着呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶嘿嘿，<delay20 />我一直想要的礼物<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到我认出里面的物品是什么的那刻，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就忍不住要笑呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
谢谢你昨天<delay8 />
和我交换礼物～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收到你送我的礼物让我很开心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年也和我交换吧～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
谢谢你昨天送我礼物～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真的很开心～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年我也想跟你交换礼物，<delay20 />
所以我要从现在起<delay8 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就开始考虑
下一件礼物是什么才行呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天<delay8 />圣诞老人和<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />你<delay8 />
都送了我礼物，我好开心呀～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来将包装好的礼物<delay20 />
拆开的过程确实也是一种乐趣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感受到的快乐都翻了好几倍呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
谢谢你昨天给我礼物～<delay frames="40" />
我真的<delay8 />非常开心～！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且，<delay8 />我也从圣诞老人那儿收到了礼物，<delay20 />
今年的平安夜
过得实在太欢快啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">我今天破例<delay20 />
把我度过圣诞节的方法<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />教给你哦～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先去散步～<delay8 />再去吃饭～<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后睡午觉，<delay8 />最后玩玩具<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃，好像跟平时比也没两样嘛～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为昨天是平安夜，<delay8 />
我想要好好招待一下圣诞老人，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay8 />就在家里等了好久<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果没能见到呢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定是看我睡着了，<delay20 />
就悄悄回去了吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>